<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Your Data Export is Ready</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .content {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      background: #10B981;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background: #059669;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .info-box {
      background: #dbeafe;
      border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .warning {
      background: #fef3c7;
      border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>‚úÖ Your Data is Ready!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello,</p>
    
    <p>Great news! Your data export from <strong>CAFEelevate</strong> has been successfully processed and is now ready for download.</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{downloadUrl}}" class="button">üì• Download Your Data</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="warning">
      <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> This download link will expire in <strong>{{expiresIn}}</strong>. Please download your data soon!
    </div>
    
    <div class="info-box">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">What's Included:</h3>
      <p>Your download is a ZIP archive containing:</p>
      <ul style="margin-bottom: 0;">
        <li><strong>README.txt</strong> - Information about the export</li>
        <li><strong>account.json</strong> - Your account details</li>
        <li><strong>orders.json</strong> - Order history</li>
        <li><strong>reservations.json</strong> - Reservation records</li>
        <li><strong>profile.json</strong> - Profile and preferences</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
    <p>After the expiration period, the download link will be automatically disabled and the export file will be permanently deleted from our servers for security.</p>
    
    <p>If you need another copy after expiration, you can request a new export from your account settings.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p><strong>Data Privacy:</strong> Your data export contains sensitive information. Please store it securely.</p>
    <p>Questions? Contact us at privacy@cafeelevate.com or visit our <a href="https://cafeelevate.com/privacy">Privacy Center</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
